{
  "stem": "24212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they got these new-- I don't know why they got us there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They needed extra work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is about February of '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "January or February.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were housed in a house which must have been something like a community center, because we were bedded down on the floor of something that-- like a theater.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a stage, actually, with a curtain, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, that's how we were bedded down, on the floor one next to another, like two of us on that rug, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mattress on mattresses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did have straw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did have a blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- the food was mostly that so-called soup with potatoes or-- it wasn't much better than Gross Rosen, because this was really the tail end of the war by this time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans knew, chances are nil that they would win the war, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sanitary conditions there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to stand in line for the john.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were maybe couple of johns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't [?see that?].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that somewhere, for the first time, I saw johns in a strange shape-- I forget where it was, whether it was right here-- that I later saw in the Orient.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The bowls had a completely different shape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I see the stage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I see a little tiny room, not bigger than maybe twice my couch-- three times my couch-- which must have been a dressing room, which a friend of mine and I sort of declared, that's our room.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody discovered it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We discovered it, and we took our mattresses there, and I remember getting hold of some scraps of newspaper with a picture of a horse.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't particularly like horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
